{"tid":1533014,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Hi international readers, please come to this thread","createTime":"2019-09-02T15:57:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-02T17:07:41.000Z","uid":42912,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"26db2a161ae6be735c3168554a8e4b4de3957d49","tid":1533014,"uid":42912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T15:57:36.000Z","msg":"To all international readers, warm welcome and thanks for visiting LIHKG. <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nTLDR; <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">We hope to make LIHKG (and hopefully Hong Kong too) a more friendly place for you. Please tweet using #LihkgForForeigners so we know you are here and can achieve it better.</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nAs you might have noticed already, LIHKG is currently available in Cantonese only and most of the content here are not friendly to international readers. The reason is that LIHKG was originally intended for the Hongkongers and did not expect such international exposure. <br />\n<br />\nHowever, there has been an increasing amount of international visitors lately. We received a lot of attention and supports from all over the world. Some of you may have registered an account already, while some of you are google translating the whole site. <em><span style=\"color: teal;\">We really appreciate all the attention and supports. </span></em><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<em><span style=\"color: teal;\">More importantly, we hope to make LIHKG a more friendly place for international readers</span></em>. If you would like to see more content in other languages, or if you would like to start a conversation here with the locals, <em><span style=\"color: red;\">please tweet using the hashtag #LihkgForForeigners to voice out. </span></em><br />\n<br />\n#LihkgForForeigners<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"703303f843d8b36f8c2ff9ce1ffde3deb75c60d4","tid":1533014,"uid":42912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T15:58:30.000Z","msg":"Push 1/10<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b2c99a0396a3ca303c0f11ffde2991cceb6b8a4","tid":1533014,"uid":42912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T15:59:23.000Z","msg":"Push 2/10<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"018c3d103f20ba098fe6886e35ab237ea6e27b56","tid":1533014,"uid":132497,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T15:59:25.000Z","msg":"希望有人幫手統籌<br />\n<br />\n[創舉] 10月1日，香港人要搞個健力士世界紀錄<br />\n<br />\n如果個日全香港人舉唔同國家既國旗，唯獨是無中共垃圾旗，搞個健力士世界紀錄，有無得諗<br />\n<br />\n香港人要入健力士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n落佢鬼國面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n[Record breaking] Oct 1, HongKongers need to break a Guiness World Record<br />\n<br />\nIf all the HongKongers carry different countries national flags, except the one of CCP, and break a Guiness World Record, sound good?<br />\n<br />\nHongKongers need to break a Guiness World Record<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nLose ChiNazi&rsquo;s face<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1532234\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1532234</a>"},{"pid":"cc442c8b1e8220a2b52a24a779b5da52d3c16a3e","tid":1533014,"uid":42912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T16:00:12.000Z","msg":"Push 3/10<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a0f8c9c6c5aeafe74d3fd37fafd372bd70712b3","tid":1533014,"uid":42912,"like":0,